 .../intel-thc-hid/intel-thc/intel-thc-dev.c   | 71 +++++++++++++++++++
 .../intel-thc-hid/intel-thc/intel-thc-dev.h   |  6 ++
 .../intel-thc-hid/intel-thc/intel-thc-dma.c   | 18 +++++
 .../intel-thc-hid/intel-thc/intel-thc-dma.h   |  3 +
